            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Определи метод класса под названием <code>introduce</code> внутри класса Pokemon.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"class\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"Pokemon\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  name = \" /><text value=\"&quot;pikachu&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"introduce\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Hi!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"37\" endIndex=\"40\" /><option startIndex=\"41\" endIndex=\"50\" /><option startIndex=\"50\" endIndex=\"51\" /><option startIndex=\"51\" endIndex=\"55\" /><option startIndex=\"55\" endIndex=\"56\" /><option startIndex=\"56\" endIndex=\"57\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>def</code>, затем <code>introduce</code>, а затем <code>(</code>, <code>self</code>, <code>)</code>, <code>:</code>.</p></body></html>"
