            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Заверши оператор отображения, который отображает переменную <code>name</code>, написав <code>self.name</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"class\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"Pokemon\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  name = \" /><text value=\"&quot;pikachu&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"introduce\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Hi!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;I am &quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" + self.name)\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"95\" endIndex=\"104\" /></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>self.name</code>.</p></body></html>"
