            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Получите доступ и вызовите метод <code>introduce</code> с использованием экземпляра класса <code>pikachu</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"class\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"Pokemon\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  name = \" /><text value=\"&quot;pikachu&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"introduce\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Hi!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;I am &quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" + self.name)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"pikachu = Pokemon()\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"pikachu.introduce()\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"127\" endIndex=\"134\" /><option startIndex=\"134\" endIndex=\"135\" /><option startIndex=\"135\" endIndex=\"144\" /><option startIndex=\"144\" endIndex=\"145\" /><option startIndex=\"145\" endIndex=\"146\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Hi!\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"I am pikachu\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>pikachu</code>, затем <code>.</code>, а затем <code>introduce</code>, <code>(</code>, <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
